  Dear Sir or Madam,

       =20
  We kindly invite you to participate in the following tender: Global=20
Real Estate, unlisted

Please follow this link to access the tender documents and submit your=20
response: LINK

If you are not interested in participating, please let us know via the=20
link above. Deadline for submissions is Tuesday, 31 March 2026 / COB=20
(Swiss time).

We frequently send invitations to market screens. To ensure you=20
receive all our emails, please make sure that=20
noreply@ams.ppcmetrics.ch is on your list of safe senders.

Our market screens (RFIs) form the first stage of our tender process=20
and apply to multiple client mandates. Submissions are stored for a=20
minimum of 12 months to ensure systematic consideration for future=20
tenders. Participation is essential to be invited to the second stage=20
(RFPs). No individual feedback is given at this stage; we will contact=20
you if you are selected for an RFP.

Thank you for your cooperation. In case you have any questions, please=20
do not reply directly to this email but get in touch with us via=20
manager.relations@ppcmetrics.ch.
